    <exercise xml:id="prob-eigenspace3">
        <statement>
            <p>
                <me>
        \begin{bmatrix}4\amp 1\\8\amp -3\end{bmatrix}.
    </me>
            </p>
        </statement>
        <answer>
            <p>
    <me>
        \lambda_1=-4,\quad\lambda_2=5.
    </me>
    
    A basis for <m>\lambda_1</m> is 
